This involves changes in DeleteCommand.java,
where it now parses a list and deletes each
person in a loop.

DeleteCommandParser.java converts any arguments
into lists.

Index.java now implements Comparable<Index>,
and overrides the hashcode function.

Three test classes have been updated to fit
with new delete command, but new tests have
not been written to test new functionality.
